FirstRand Chief Executive Officer Nxasana Sells $2.5 Million of Securities

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-04-26T10:53:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/firstrand-chief-executive-officer-nxasana-sells-2-5-million-of-securities.html
FirstRand Ltd. (FSR)  said Chief Executive
Officer Sizwe Nxasana sold 16.45 million rand worth of stock at
about 19.97 rand apiece on April 21.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  